        <h2>Birth Doula Care</h2>
        <p>
          Your birth is one of the most profound moments of your life. As your birth doula,
          I provide unwavering, continuous support from early labor through delivery and the
          first hours with your newborn.
        </p>
        <p>
          I work alongside your medical team — never replacing them — to ensure you feel
          informed and confident in every decision made during your birth.
        </p>
        <strong>What's included:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Two prenatal visits to discuss your birth preferences and build our relationship</li>
          <li>On-call availability from 37 weeks until labor begins</li>
          <li>Continuous labor support from early labor through delivery</li>
          <li>Physical comfort measures (positioning, counter-pressure, breathing guidance)</li>
          <li>Emotional reassurance and encouragement for you and your partner</li>
          <li>Assistance communicating your wishes to your care team</li>
          <li>One postpartum visit (within two weeks of birth) for reflection and resource sharing</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:1.5rem; display:inline-block;">Inquire About Birth Support</a>
